                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Hana's Hundreds attempt to trample all foes in their way. The team Forms Up and Strides twice, moving through the space of Medium or smaller creatures. Each creature the team moves through takes[[/r 4d8+14 #bludgeoning]]{4d8+14 bludgeoning damage} (<span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-traits=\"damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Rune Them Over! DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"33\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span> save). On a critical failure, the creature is also knocked @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Prone]{Prone}.</p>"
